\(a=(a_{n})_{M&lt;n\leq M+N}\) of complex numbers. We let</p>

\[S(\alpha)=\sum_{M&lt;n\leq M+N}a_{n}(\alpha n).\]

<p>Then</p>

\[\sum_{r\leq R}|S(\alpha)|^{2}\leq(N-1+\delta^{-1})\left\Vert a\right\Vert ^{2},\]

<p>where \(\delta\) is the minimum distance between different \(\alpha_{i}\) in
